name: MXDiagnosticPayload
desc: An object that encapsulates a diagnostic report.

items.name: var crashDiagnostics: [MXCrashDiagnostic]?
items.desc: The diagnostic reports for app crashes during the reporting period.

items.name: var cpuExceptionDiagnostics: [MXCPUExceptionDiagnostic]?
items.desc: The diagnostic reports for fatal and nonfatal CPU exceptions for the app during the reporting period.

items.name: var hangDiagnostics: [MXHangDiagnostic]?
items.desc: The diagnostic reports for times when the app was too busy to handle input responsively during the reporting period.

items.name: var diskWriteExceptionDiagnostics: [MXDiskWriteExceptionDiagnostic]?
items.desc: The diagnostic reports for disk write exceptions for the app during the reporting period.

items.name: func jsonRepresentation() -> Data
items.desc: Returns the contents of the payload in JSON format.

items.name: func dictionaryRepresentation() -> [AnyHashable : Any]
items.desc: Returns the results of the payload as a dictionary.

items.name: var timeStampBegin: Date
items.desc: The starting time of the reporting period.

items.name: var timeStampEnd: Date
items.desc: The ending time of the reporting period.
